#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.174"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.174:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.174:0.2"
msgid "14. Oghavagga"
msgstr "14. Floods"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.174:0.3"
msgid "174. Ganthasutta"
msgstr "174. Personal Ties"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.60"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.174:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, ganthā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four ties."

msgctxt "sn45.174:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn45.174:1.3"
msgid ""
"Abhijjhā kāyagantho, byāpādo kāyagantho, sīlabbataparāmāso kāyagantho, "
"idaṃsaccābhiniveso kāyagantho—"
msgstr ""
"The personal ties to covetousness, ill will, misapprehension of precepts and "
"observances, and the insistence that this is the only truth."

msgctxt "sn45.174:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro ganthā."
msgstr "These are the four ties."

msgctxt "sn45.174:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ganthānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya "
"pahānāya … pe … ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, "
"complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these four ties.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.174:1.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
